name: CFURLBookmarkResolutionOptions
desc: Type for bookmark data resolution options.

items.name: static var cfBookmarkResolutionWithoutMountingMask: CFURLBookmarkResolutionOptions
items.desc: Specifies that no volume should be mounted during resolution of the bookmark data.

items.name: static var cfBookmarkResolutionWithoutUIMask: CFURLBookmarkResolutionOptions
items.desc: Specifies that no UI feedback accompany resolution of the bookmark data.

items.name: static var cfurlBookmarkResolutionWithSecurityScope: CFURLBookmarkResolutionOptions
items.desc: Specifies that the security scope, applied to the bookmark when it was created, should be used during resolution of the bookmark data.
